msgid "This utility should only be used in live mode!"
msgstr "Dette værktøj bør kun bruges i live-tilstand!"

msgid ""
"<span font='12'>This tool should be used in live mode and to restore the Manjaro boot\n"
"installed on HD or SSD.</span>\n"
"\n"
"<span font='12' foreground='red'>If the installed system is starting correctly there are no "
"problems in the boot, so it is\n"
"better not to continue the use of this tool.</span>\n"
"<span font='10' foreground='gray'>Probably also work with other Linux distributions.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='12'>Dette værktøj skal bruges i live-tilstand og til at gendanne Manjaro-boot\n"
"installeret på HD eller SSD.</span> <span font='12' foreground='red'>Hvis det installerede system "
"starter korrekt, er der ingen problemer i opstarten, så det er\n"
"Bedre ikke at fortsætte brugen af dette værktøj.</span> <span font='10' "
"foreground='gray'>Sandsynligvis også arbejde med andre Linux-distributioner.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Vil du fortsætte?\n"
"\n"
"\n"

msgid "Restore Boot, Grub and Initrd"
msgstr "Gendan Boot, Grub og Initrd"

msgid "Wait..."
msgstr "Vent..."

msgid "I didn't find any Linux installed on this computer, canceled process.\n"
msgstr "Jeg fandt ikke nogen Linux installeret på denne computer, annulleret proces."

msgid ""
"The boot in live mode is using EFI mode, but <span foreground='red'>I didn't find any EFI "
"partition</span> on this computer,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in Legacy or BIOS mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"Opstart i live-tilstand bruger EFI-tilstand, men <span foreground='red'>jeg fandt ikke nogen "
"EFI-partition</span> på denne computer,\n"
"sandsynligvis GRUB restaurering vil ikke fungere.\n"
"\n"
"Prøv at genstarte og via computeren BIOS gøre boot i Legacy eller BIOS-tilstand.\n"
"\n"
"Vil du prøve selv med lidt sandsynlighed for at arbejde?"

msgid ""
"Boot in live mode is using Legacy mode, also called BIOS,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>but I found at least one EFI partition on this computer</span>,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in EFI mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"Opstart i live-tilstand bruger Legacy-tilstand, også kaldet BIOS,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>men jeg fandt mindst en EFI-partition på denne computer</span>,\n"
"sandsynligvis GRUB restaurering vil ikke fungere.\n"
"\n"
"Prøv at genstarte og gennem computeren BIOS gøre boot i EFI-tilstand.\n"
"\n"
"Vil du prøve selv med lidt sandsynlighed for at arbejde?"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one EFI partition, select which one should use:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Vælg en indstilling:</span>\n"
"\n"
"Jeg fandt mere end en EFI-partition, vælg hvilken der skal bruge:"

msgid "No EFI partition selected, canceled process."
msgstr "Ingen EFI-partition valgt, annulleret proces."

msgid "Restore the Boot, Grub and Initrd "
msgstr "Gendan boot, grub og initrd "

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one Linux installed on this computer, select which one should restore the boot:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Vælg en indstilling:</span>\n"
"\n"
"Jeg fandt mere end en Linux installeret på denne computer, vælg hvilken der skal gendanne boot:"

msgid "No selected partition, canceled process."
msgstr "Ingen valgt partition, annulleret proces."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"I found more than one storage device, select which one should record the boot:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Vælg en indstilling:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"Jeg fandt mere end en lagerenhed, vælg hvilken der skal optage opstarten:"

msgid "Disk"
msgstr "Skive"

msgid "Size"
msgstr "Størrelse"

msgid "Name"
msgstr "Navn"

msgid "Partition table"
msgstr "Partitionstabellen"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>    \n"
"\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span>  LEGACY/BIOS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected disk:</span> $DISK_SELECTED\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk partition table:</span> $DISK_TABLE\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk Size:</span> $DISK_SIZE\n"
"   \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Bekræft data:</span>    \n"
"\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Opstartstilstand:</span>  LEGACY/BIOS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Markeret disk:</span> $DISK_SELECTED\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Diskpartitionstabel:</span> $DISK_TABLE\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Diskstørrelse:</span> $DISK_SIZE\n"
"   \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valgt partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valgt system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partitionsformat:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Vil du fortsætte?"

msgid "Your computer is not connected to the internet, options 2 and 3 need internet to work."
msgstr ""
"Din computer har ikke forbindelse til internettet, mulighed 2 og 3 har brug for internet for at "
"fungere."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways (<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or "
"Complete</span>),if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Vælg den ønskede indstilling:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restaurering kan udføres på 3 måder (<span foreground='gray'>enkel, mellemliggende eller "
"komplet</span>), hvis du er i tvivl, prøv den første\n"
"mulighed, genstart computeren og se om du løste.\n"
"\n"
"Hvis problemet fortsætter, kan du prøve de andre muligheder."

msgid "Option"
msgstr "Valgmulighed"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beskrivelse: __________"

msgid "Simple, just record the grub again at the beginning of the disk."
msgstr "Enkelt, bare optag grub igen i begyndelsen af disken."

msgid ""
"Intermediate, reinstalls the GRUB package in the partition, generates the configuration and updates "
"Initrd."
msgstr ""
"Mellemliggende, geninstallerer GRUB-pakken i partitionen, genererer konfigurationen og opdaterer "
"Initrd."

msgid ""
"Complete, performs the stages of the intermediate restoration, updates the system and checks if the "
"LTS kernel is installed."
msgstr ""
"Komplet, udfører stadierne i den mellemliggende restaurering, opdaterer systemet og kontrollerer, "
"om LTS-kernen er installeret."

msgid "Interactive, opens a terminal within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktiv, åbner en terminal i det valgte system."

msgid "Interactive, opens a TUI control center within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktiv, åbner et TUI-kontrolcenter i det valgte system."

msgid "Collect useful logs from installed system"
msgstr "Indsaml nyttige logfiler fra installeret system"

msgid "Interactive, opens the package manager within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktiv, åbner pakkehåndteringen i det valgte system."

msgid "Done!"
msgstr "Gjort!"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span> EFI\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>EFI partition:</span> $EFI_PARTITION\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Bekræft data:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Opstartstilstand:</span> EFI\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>EFI-partition:</span> $EFI_PARTITION\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valgt partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valgt system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partitionsformat:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Vil du fortsætte?"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways(<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or Complete</span>), "
"if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Vælg den ønskede indstilling:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Gendannelse kan udføres på 3 måder(<span foreground='gray'>Enkel, mellemliggende eller "
"komplet</span>), hvis du er i tvivl, så prøv den første\n"
"mulighed, genstart computeren og se om du løste.\n"
"\n"
"Hvis problemet fortsætter, kan du prøve de andre muligheder."
